        <item>
            <title>【评测】ROG Zephyrus G16 轻薄电竞笔电，再见厚底劲嘈风扇，超薄宁静机内置 RTX 4070</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/25/rog-zephyrus-g16/notebook/notebook-review/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rog-zephyrus-g16</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/25/rog-zephyrus-g16/notebook/notebook-review/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Ultrabook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[笔电测试]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[asus]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Game Pass]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gaming laptop]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[pc game]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG Zephyrus G16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1282990</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>以前讲到电竞手提电脑，好多朋友都会联想到超厚底机身，重量大到不可能带出街，而且在打机时风扇需要发出轰音维持散热。今次我们要睇的华硕最新 ROG Zephyrus G16 系列，就打破了以往电竞手提电脑又厚又重的定律，融合轻薄设计与效能，搭载 AMD Ryzen AI 9 HX 370 处理器，并配备 RTX 40 系列显示卡，机身厚度只有 14.9mm（最薄部份），重量也只有 1.85 kg。笔电兼备 16 吋 OLED 荧幕，以及和机面背光灯设计，极之适合追求流动打机畅快感受的朋友仔，当然也适合需要随时随地带住强大电脑外出工作的创作者朋友。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283033 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04408-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04408-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04408.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283022 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04429-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04429-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04429.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ROG Zephyrus G16 拥有高效处理器与影像处理器，但给用家超薄超轻机身</p><h2>轻薄设计与高效能完美结合</h2><p>ROG Zephyrus G16 GA605W 以铝合金材质制作，机身通过 CNC 精密加工，维持轻薄便携。笔电提供「日蚀灰」与「铂月银」两种配色，重量仅约 1.85 公斤，最薄位置厚度只有 14.9mm，而最厚处也只厚 16.9 mm。特别的是手提电脑搭配的 200W 变压器，同样比以往的电竞手提电脑细好多，电脑再加火牛的总重量约，为 2.4 kg，适合长时间携带，或者拿去旅行工干，随时随地打机。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283030 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04406-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04406-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04406.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283032 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04409-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04409-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04409.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1283024 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04388-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04388-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04388.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲电脑跟来的变压器比同类型电脑细得多，只有约一部 iPhone Pro Max 的大小</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1283025 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04389-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04389-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04389.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲变压器连电线整体重量也只约为 600g</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1283026 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04390-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04390-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04390.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而电脑本身则只重约 1800g，为一部轻盈电竞手提电脑</p><p>机身上盖引入了「Slash 灯效」，简单来说就是比较沉实的灯光条，以多个 LED 灯所组成。它支援 15 种自订灯光模式。无论在电脑运作以至休眠时，都可发出闪灯效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283028 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04402-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04402-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04402.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283029 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04401-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04401-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04401.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283034 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04439-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04439-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04439.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>打开机盖后你即刻会看到面积大得惊人的触控板。它长阔分别为 15cm x 10cm，比上代触控板面积提升 37%，可说是专门为创意工作者度身订造。在户外工作例如需要放大相片，检视影片，这个大型触控板都可令操作更得心应手。不过留意它实体有 click 感的点击按钮的部份为下半部，而上半部都可以轻触式点击操作电脑。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283020 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04463-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04463-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04463.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲电脑最薄处距离桌面只有约 1.65cm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283066 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04458-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04458-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04458.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以前意想不到电竞手提电脑都可以这么薄</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1283019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04471-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04471-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04471.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></p><p>键盘的部份也合符游戏玩家以至办公用家的工作需要，键帽尺寸增大 12% 之外，即使在这么薄的机身这部 GA605W 也配置了 RGB 背光灯设计。右上角配备玻璃材质电源键，开机那一刻开始已感受到贴身的操作感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283067 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04432-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04432-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04432.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲连电源键的手感都十分考究</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283060 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04415-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04415-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04415.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配备 RGB 背光键盘</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283061 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04410-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04410-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04410.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲极大面积触控板带来灵活电脑操作感</p><h2><span lang="EN-US">ROG Intelligent Cooling (</span>智能散热技术<span lang="EN-US">) </span>改善游戏速度与风扇噪音平衡</h2><p>ROG Zephyrus G16 机内的应用程式，利用 AI 协助电脑为用家提升效能。它可细致调整 CPU 与 GPU 的频率，以及在风扇的效率，让用家在极需要处理效能时，能发挥电脑的最佳表现之余，而同时可控制散热系统，获得更宁静的使用体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283004 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241218213455-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241218213455-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241218213455.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283040 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04383-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04383-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04383.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而在一间底噪为 45dB 的房间中，电脑全速运作时噪音也只升到约 58dB，可说是不太嘈吵的音量，在电竞手提电脑来说表现相当不错</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1283013 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04446-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04446-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc04446.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲经过智能调节，在不完全运作的情况下，可减低风扇噪音</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
