            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年折机卖到成行成市，花款亦愈来愈多，令大家看到眼花瞭乱。但其实一部电话花款及功能再多，一般人实际使用时也只是用来影相、上网揾料、打机……简单来说就是讲求实用性。HUAWEI 最近就在香港推出 HUAWEI Mate X6 这部全新「大折」，究竟使用起来感受如何？就让我们为大家分享一下用后体验吧。</p><h2>相关影片 :</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_49946"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YGSR-e4rPJQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>超轻薄唔玩花巧实用先行</h2><p>今次 HUAWEI 推出的 Mate X6「大折」，可说是继承了上代港行「大折」HUAWEI Mate X3 的设计 ID：大玩纤巧轻薄，重量只有 239g，摊开使用时机身厚度只有 5mm 左右，即使折叠起来厚度也只是 10mm，加上边位采用微弧设计，拿上手完全不觉刮手，轻薄设计亦令大家折叠时单手握机使用都无问题，而摊开以大荧幕使用，双手长时间拿著手机也不会容易感到疲累，手感十分不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_46huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_46huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_46huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次 HUAWEI 推出的 HUAWEI Mate X6「大折」，外形与上代港行「大折」HUAWEI Mate X3 相比可说是拥有相同设计 ID。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_20huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_20huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_20huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身依然十分薄身，折叠起来时机身厚度只是 10mm。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_23huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_23huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_23huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而展开机身使用时机身厚度更薄至只有 5mm 左右，超级薄身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283158" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_03huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_03huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122022_54_03huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这个纤巧设计，令大家拿 HUAWEI Mate X6 外出使用时十分轻松，长时间双手拿机也不会易感疲倦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_41huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_41huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_41huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配色方面，HUAWEI Mate X6 设有 3 种设计，分别是采用素皮机背的寰宇红及曜石黑，以及采用织锦纤维物料机背的星云灰。</p><p>除了纤巧之余，HUAWEI Mate X6 亦设有内外两块大尺寸的 OLED 荧幕，折叠时可以使用机面的 6.45 吋荧幕，大家可以见到边框十分窄，用尽所有空间；而摊开手机就可以透过 7.93 吋折叠式 OLED 荧幕使用手机，感觉就像一部小型平板，令大家可以在更广阔荧幕上进行不同工作，甚至同时使用多个程式，提升多工作业效率。（这部分后文会再作详述。）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_12huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_12huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_12huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身支援 IPX8 抗水功能，使用时更安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1283163" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_10huaw-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_10huaw-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024122023_03_10huaw.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机内亦搭配了 2000W/m．K 超高导热石墨烯 3D 液冷 VC 立体散热结构，散热表现有一定保证。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
